If Gmsh is generating only a surface mesh instead of a 3D mesh, you likely need to specify or enable volume meshing. Here are some steps and tips to ensure you get a 3D mesh:


Define the Volume:
Ensure that you have defined the volume (3D region) in your geometry. In Gmsh, volumes are defined using the Volume keyword.
// Example: Define a simple box volume
Point(1) = {0, 0, 0, 1};
Point(2) = {1, 0, 0, 1};
Point(3) = {1, 1, 0, 1};
Point(4) = {0, 1, 0, 1};
Point(5) = {0, 0, 1, 1};
Point(6) = {1, 0, 1, 1};
Point(7) = {1, 1, 1, 1};
Point(8) = {0, 1, 1, 1};

Line(1) = {1, 2};
Line(2) = {2, 3};
Line(3) = {3, 4};
Line(4) = {4, 1};
Line(5) = {1, 5};
Line(6) = {2, 6};
Line(7) = {3, 7};
Line(8) = {4, 8};
Line(9) = {5, 6};
Line(10) = {6, 7};
Line(11) = {7, 8};
Line(12) = {8, 5};

Line Loop(13) = {1, 2, 3, 4};
Plane Surface(14) = {13};

Line Loop(15) = {5, -9, -8, 12};
Plane Surface(16) = {15};

Line Loop(17) = {6, -10, -7, 9};
Plane Surface(18) = {17};

Line Loop(19) = {7, -11, -6, 10};
Plane Surface(20) = {19};

Line Loop(21) = {8, -12, -5, 11};
Plane Surface(22) = {21};

Surface Loop(23) = {14, 16, 18, 20, 22};
Volume(24) = {23};


Mesh the Volume:
Ensure that you generate the volume mesh. In the Gmsh GUI, you can do this by going to the mesh options and selecting 3D.
In the .geo file, you can specify the meshing command as follows:
Mesh 3;


Check Mesh Options:
In the Gmsh GUI, you can go to Tools -> Options -> Mesh -> General and ensure that the "Mesh dimension" is set to 3.


Ensure All Boundaries are Defined:
Make sure that all the surfaces that form the boundary of the volume are properly defined and connected.


Physical Groups (Optional but recommended):
Define physical groups for the volume. This helps Gmsh understand what you want to mesh and can improve meshing performance.
Physical Volume("MyVolume") = {24};


By following these steps, Gmsh should generate a 3D mesh instead of just a surface mesh. If you still encounter issues, please share your .geo file or the specific error messages you are seeing for more tailored assistance.
